{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"8463","heading":"Pay-for-performance projects","label":"8463 Pay-for-performance projects","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/ch103/schI/ptE","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","References in TextThe Social Security Act, referred to in subsec. (d)(1), is , . Subtitle C of title XX of the Act is classified generally to division C (§ 1397n et seq.) of subchapter XX of chapter 7 of Title 42, The Public Health and Welfare. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see and Tables.act Aug. 14, 1935, ch. 53149 Stat. 620section 1305 of Title 42"],"amendments":["References in TextThe Social Security Act, referred to in subsec. (d)(1), is , . Subtitle C of title XX of the Act is classified generally to division C (§ 1397n et seq.) of subchapter XX of chapter 7 of Title 42, The Public Health and Welfare. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see and Tables.act Aug. 14, 1935, ch. 53149 Stat. 620section 1305 of Title 42"],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"Definitions","label":"a Definitions","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"Independent evaluator","label":"1 Independent evaluator","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The term “independent evaluator” means an individual or entity, including an institution of higher education, that is selected by the pay-for-performance beneficiary and pay-for-performance investor, as applicable, or by the pay-for-performance project developer, in consultation with the Secretary of Agriculture, to make the determinations and prepare the reports required under subsection (e).","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"National Forest System land","label":"2 National Forest System land","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The term “National Forest System land” means land in the National Forest System (as defined in ).section 1609(a) of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":"Pay-for-performance agreement","label":"3 Pay-for-performance agreement","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fa%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a/3/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fa%2F3%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a/3/A/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a/3/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fa%2F3%2FA%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"not less than 1 year; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a/3/A/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a/3/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fa%2F3%2FA%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"not more than 20 years; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a/3/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fa%2F3%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a/3/B/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a/3/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fa%2F3%2FB%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the Secretary of Agriculture; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a/3/B/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a/3/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fa%2F3%2FB%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a pay-for-performance beneficiary or pay-for-performance project developer.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"4","heading":"Pay-for-performance beneficiary","label":"4 Pay-for-performance beneficiary","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a/4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fa%2F4","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a/4/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a/4","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fa%2F4%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"repays capital loaned upfront by a pay-for-performance investor, based on a project outcome specified in a pay-for-performance agreement; or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a/4/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a/4","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fa%2F4%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"provides capital directly for costs associated with a pay-for-performance project.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"5","heading":"Pay-for-performance investor","label":"5 Pay-for-performance investor","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a/5","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fa%2F5","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The term “pay-for-performance investor” means a State or local government, an Indian Tribe, or a nonprofit or for-profit organization that provides upfront loaned capital for a pay-for-performance project with the expectation of a financial return dependent on a project outcome.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"6","heading":"Pay-for-performance project","label":"6 Pay-for-performance project","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a/6","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fa%2F6","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a/6/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a/6","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fa%2F6%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"would provide or enhance a recreational opportunity;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a/6/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a/6","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fa%2F6%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a/6/B/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a/6/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fa%2F6%2FB%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"National Forest System land; or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a/6/B/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a/6/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fa%2F6%2FB%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"other land, if the activities would benefit National Forest System land (including a recreational use of National Forest System land); and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":null,"label":"C","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a/6/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a/6","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fa%2F6%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a/6/C/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a/6/C","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fa%2F6%2FC%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"loaned capital from a pay-for-performance investor to cover upfront costs associated with a pay-for-performance project, with the loaned capital repaid by a pay-for-performance beneficiary at a rate of return dependent on a project outcome, as measured by an independent evaluator; or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a/6/C/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a/6/C","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fa%2F6%2FC%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"capital directly from a pay-for-performance beneficiary to support costs associated with a pay-for-performance project in an amount based on an anticipated project outcome.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"7","heading":"Pay-for-performance project developer","label":"7 Pay-for-performance project developer","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a/7","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fa%2F7","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The term “pay-for-performance project developer” means a nonprofit or for-profit organization that serves as an intermediary to assist in developing or implementing a pay-for-performance agreement or a pay-for-performance project.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"8","heading":"Project outcome","label":"8 Project outcome","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a/8","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fa%2F8","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The term “project outcome” means a measurable, beneficial result (whether economic, environmental, or social) that is attributable to a pay-for-performance project and described in a pay-for-performance agreement.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Establishment of pilot program","label":"b Establishment of pilot program","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Secretary of Agriculture shall establish a pilot program in accordance with this section to carry out 1 or more pay-for-performance projects.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":"Pay-for-performance projects","label":"c Pay-for-performance projects","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fc","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"In general","label":"1 In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/c/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fc%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/c/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/c/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fc%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the Secretary of Agriculture; or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/c/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/c/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fc%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/c/1/B/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/c/1/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fc%2F1%2FB%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the Secretary of Agriculture shall approve the implementation by the pay-for-performance project developer or third party; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/c/1/B/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/c/1/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fc%2F1%2FB%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the implementation is in accordance with applicable law.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Relation to land management plans","label":"2 Relation to land management plans","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/c/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fc%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"A pay-for-performance project carried out under this section shall be consistent with any applicable land management plan developed under .section 1604 of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":"Ownership","label":"3 Ownership","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/c/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fc%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":"New improvements","label":"A New improvements","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/c/3/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/c/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fc%2F3%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The United States shall have title to any improvements installed on National Forest System land as part of a pay-for-performance project.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":"Existing improvements","label":"B Existing improvements","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/c/3/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/c/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fc%2F3%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/c/3/B/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/c/3/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fc%2F3%2FB%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"any federally owned improvements involved in the pay-for-performance project; or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/c/3/B/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/c/3/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fc%2F3%2FB%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the underlying land.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"4","heading":"Savings clause","label":"4 Savings clause","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/c/4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fc%2F4","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The carrying out of any action for a pay-for-performance project does not provide any right to any party to a pay-for-performance agreement.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"5","heading":"Potential conflicts","label":"5 Potential conflicts","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/c/5","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fc%2F5","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Before approving a pay-for-performance project under this section, the Secretary of Agriculture shall consider and seek to avoid potential conflicts (including economic competition) with any existing written authorized use.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"d","heading":"Project agreements","label":"d Project agreements","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fd","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"In general","label":"1 In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fd%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Notwithstanding the Act of (, chapter 131; ), or subtitle C of title XX of the Social Security Act ( et seq.), in carrying out the pilot program under this section, the Secretary of Agriculture may enter into a pay-for-performance agreement under which a pay-for-performance beneficiary, pay-for-performance investor, or pay-for-performance project developer agrees to pay for or finance all or part of a pay-for-performance project.June 30, 191438 Stat. 43016 U.S.C. 49842 U.S.C. 1397n","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Size limitation","label":"2 Size limitation","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fd%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Secretary of Agriculture may not enter into a pay-for-performance agreement under the pilot program under this section for a pay-for-performance project valued at more than $15,000,000.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":"Financing","label":"3 Financing","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fd%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":"In general","label":"A In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/3/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fd%2F3%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"A pay-for-performance agreement shall specify the amounts that a pay-for-performance beneficiary or a pay-for-performance project developer agrees to pay to a pay-for-performance investor or a pay-for-performance project developer, as appropriate, in the event of an independent evaluator determining pursuant to subsection (e) the degree to which a project outcome has been achieved.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":"Eligible payments","label":"B Eligible payments","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/3/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fd%2F3%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/3/B/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/3/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fd%2F3%2FB%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subclause","nativeType":"subclause","number":"I","heading":null,"label":"I","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/3/B/i/I","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/3/B/i","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fd%2F3%2FB%2Fi%2FI","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the respective contributions of the parties under the pay-for-performance agreement; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subclause","nativeType":"subclause","number":"II","heading":null,"label":"II","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/3/B/i/II","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/3/B/i","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fd%2F3%2FB%2Fi%2FII","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the economic, environmental, or social benefits derived from the project outcomes; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/3/B/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/3/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fd%2F3%2FB%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subclause","nativeType":"subclause","number":"I","heading":null,"label":"I","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/3/B/ii/I","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/3/B/ii","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fd%2F3%2FB%2Fii%2FI","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a percentage of the estimated value of a project outcome;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subclause","nativeType":"subclause","number":"II","heading":null,"label":"II","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/3/B/ii/II","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/3/B/ii","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fd%2F3%2FB%2Fii%2FII","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a percentage of the estimated cost savings to the pay-for-performance beneficiary or the Secretary of Agriculture derived from a project outcome;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subclause","nativeType":"subclause","number":"III","heading":null,"label":"III","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/3/B/ii/III","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/3/B/ii","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fd%2F3%2FB%2Fii%2FIII","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a percentage of the enhanced revenue to the pay-for-performance beneficiary or the Secretary of Agriculture derived from a project outcome; or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subclause","nativeType":"subclause","number":"IV","heading":null,"label":"IV","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/3/B/ii/IV","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/3/B/ii","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fd%2F3%2FB%2Fii%2FIV","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a percentage of the cost of the pay-for-performance project.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":"Forest service financial assistance","label":"C Forest service financial assistance","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/3/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fd%2F3%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/3/C/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/3/C","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fd%2F3%2FC%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subclause","nativeType":"subclause","number":"I","heading":null,"label":"I","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/3/C/i/I","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/3/C/i","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fd%2F3%2FC%2Fi%2FI","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the pay-for-performance project would provide a cost savings to the United States;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subclause","nativeType":"subclause","number":"II","heading":null,"label":"II","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/3/C/i/II","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/3/C/i","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fd%2F3%2FC%2Fi%2FII","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the funding would accelerate the pace of implementation of an activity previously planned to be completed by the Secretary of Agriculture; or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subclause","nativeType":"subclause","number":"III","heading":null,"label":"III","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/3/C/i/III","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/3/C/i","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fd%2F3%2FC%2Fi%2FIII","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the funding would accelerate the scale of implementation of an activity previously planned to be completed by the Secretary of Agriculture; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/3/C/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/3/C","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fd%2F3%2FC%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the contribution of the Secretary of Agriculture has a value that is not more than 50 percent of the total cost of the pay-for-performance project.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"D","heading":"Special account","label":"D Special account","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/3/D","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fd%2F3%2FD","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/3/D/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/3/D","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fd%2F3%2FD%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"shall be retained in a separate fund in the Treasury to be used solely for pay-for-performance projects; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/3/D/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/3/D","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fd%2F3%2FD%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"shall remain available until expended and without further appropriation.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"4","heading":"Maintenance and decommissioning of pay-for-performance project improvements","label":"4 Maintenance and decommissioning of pay-for-performance project improvements","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fd%2F4","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/4/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/4","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fd%2F4%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"include a plan for maintaining any capital improvement constructed as part of a pay-for-performance project after the date on which the pay-for-performance project is completed; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/4/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/4","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fd%2F4%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/4/B/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/4/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fd%2F4%2FB%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"at the end of the useful life of the improvements;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/4/B/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/4/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fd%2F4%2FB%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"if the improvements no longer serve the purpose for which the improvements were developed; or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"iii","heading":null,"label":"iii","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/4/B/iii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/4/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fd%2F4%2FB%2Fiii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"if the pay-for-performance project fails.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"5","heading":"Termination of pay-for-performance project agreements","label":"5 Termination of pay-for-performance project agreements","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d/5","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fd%2F5","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Secretary of Agriculture may unilaterally terminate a pay-for-performance agreement, in whole or in part, for any program year beginning after the program year during which the Secretary of Agriculture provides to each party to the pay-for-performance agreement a notice of the termination.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"e","heading":"Independent evaluations","label":"e Independent evaluations","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/e","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fe","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"Progress reports","label":"1 Progress reports","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/e/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/e","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fe%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/e/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/e/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fe%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"by not later than 2 years after the date on which the pay-for-performance agreement is executed, and at least once every 2 years thereafter, a written report that summarizes the progress that has been made in achieving each project outcome; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/e/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/e/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fe%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/e/1/B/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/e/1/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fe%2F1%2FB%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"summarizes the results of the evaluation conducted by the independent evaluator to determine whether a payment should be made pursuant to the pay-for-performance agreement; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/e/1/B/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/e/1/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fe%2F1%2FB%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"analyzes the reasons why a project outcome was achieved or was not achieved.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Final reports","label":"2 Final reports","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/e/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/e","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fe%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/e/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/e/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fe%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"an evaluation of the effects of the pay-for-performance project with respect to each project outcome;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/e/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/e/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fe%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a determination of whether the pay-for-performance project has met each project outcome; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":null,"label":"C","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/e/2/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/e/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fe%2F2%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the amount of the payments made for the pay-for-performance project pursuant to subsection (d)(3)(A).","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"f","heading":"Additional Forest Service-provided assistance","label":"f Additional Forest Service-provided assistance","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/f","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Ff","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"Technical assistance","label":"1 Technical assistance","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/f/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/f","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Ff%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Secretary of Agriculture may provide technical assistance to facilitate pay-for-performance project development, such as planning, permitting, site preparation, and design work.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Consultants","label":"2 Consultants","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/f/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/f","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Ff%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/f/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/f/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Ff%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"to conduct a feasibility analysis of a proposed pay-for-performance project;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/f/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/f/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Ff%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"to assist in the development, implementation, or evaluation of a proposed pay-for-performance project or a pay-for-performance agreement; or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":null,"label":"C","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/f/2/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/f/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Ff%2F2%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"to assist with an environmental analysis of a proposed pay-for-performance project.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"g","heading":"Savings clause","label":"g Savings clause","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/g","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fg","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Secretary of Agriculture shall approve a record of decision, decision notice, or decision memo for any activities to be carried out on National Forest System land as part of a pay-for-performance project before the Secretary of Agriculture may enter into a pay-for-performance agreement involving the applicable pay-for-performance project.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"h","heading":"Duration of pilot program","label":"h Duration of pilot program","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/h","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fh","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"Sunset","label":"1 Sunset","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/h/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/h","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fh%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The authority to enter into a pay-for-performance agreement under this section terminates on the date that is 7 years after .January 4, 2025","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Savings clause","label":"2 Savings clause","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/h/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s8463/h","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs8463%2Fh%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Nothing in paragraph (1) affects any pay-for-performance project agreement entered into by the Secretary of Agriculture under this section before the date described in that paragraph.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]}
